Odaily Planet Daily News According to Spot On Chain monitoring, a whale deposited 3.92 million USDC to HyperLiquid in the past 17 hours to buy more HYPE and open a long position.
Currently, the whale holds 241,876 HYPE (about 3.53 million US dollars) with a floating loss of about 1.47 million US dollars;
At the same time, it holds a long position of 320,333 HYPE at a price of 14.46 US dollars (3x leverage);
There are also 5080 HYPEs with limit orders set between 14.05 US dollars and 14.15 US dollars.
